name: Kevin SILAS, Petitioner v. Sheila SKIPPER-WOODS [sic], Judge of Common Pleas Court, Philadelphia County, Pennsylvania, Respondent

parties: Kevin SILAS, Petitioner v. Sheila SKIPPER-WOODS [sic], Judge of Common Pleas Court, Philadelphia County, Pennsylvania, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 29th day of May, 2014, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
